/ Tang &amp; Li&quot; [red handwritten label] (SHNU). Paratypes.Zhejiang: 3♂♂3♀♀, same data as the holotype (1 pair in MHNG, remaining in SHNU); 2♂♂1♀, Anji County, Longwangshan, N 30°24', E 119°21', alt. 1200-1500m, 8.IV.2012, Bi, Hu &amp; Yin leg. (1♂ in CBWX, remaining in SHNU); 2♀♀, 
